od of time, you'll have virtually unlimited focus, project a mirror image, or release a shock wave that will knock back all attacking enemies.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/489080/extras/crystal_haste_64.png?t=1475644873\" ><br>Crystals are an incredible source of power, and are very valuable. For defeating realm guardians, your reward is paid in crystals instead of etherium. You'll need them for the crystal spells during difficult missions, and they're used to purchase the highest level of upgrades, so use them wisely. There's no shortage of guardians, and at least one can be found every day. You can also earn crystals through your achievements, which are tracked in the Conquest room.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/489080/extras/lightning_ball_64.png?t=1475644873\" ><br>Your journey mastering the elements and conquering the realms, eventually to face the legendary guardian of the Obsidian Lair is about to begin.<br><br>Are you prepared?<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/489080/extras/App_Icon_64.png?t=1475644873\" >",
